title: Kim Davis Took Her Position With Intent To Deny Marriage Licenses
text: In defense of Kim Davis, conservatives often point out that ‘the definition of marriage changed’ after Davis, the Kentucky County Clerk who has been at the center of a battle between the right to marry and the right to prevent others from doing things based on religious belief, took office.
